column2: SELECT m.id, m.ra AS ra1, m.dec AS dec1, n.objid, n.distance, q.TargetQsoTargeted, q.SpecQsoConfirmed, q.SpecQsoUnknown, q.SpecQsoLargeZ, q.SpecQsoTargeted, q.BestQsoTargeted into mydb.GreenPeas_QSO from mydb.GreenPeas AS m CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq (m.ra, m.dec, #) AS n JOIN QsoCatalogAll AS q ON n.objid = q.targetobjid
